  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a descriptive, retrospective, multi-center, cross-sectional and observational
      epidemiological study of incidence and prevalence of juvenile dermatomyositis in Alsace from
      2000 to 2015. Alsace is a French region with a low migratory flow
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
